<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>비밀번호 변경</title>
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    body {
      min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1f36 0%, #2d3561 50%, #1a1f36 100%);
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', 'Malgun Gothic', sans-serif;
    }

    .wrap { width: 100%; max-width: 440px; padding: 16px; }

    .card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      border-radius: 20px; padding: 48px 40px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(20px); box-shadow: 0 24px 48px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
    }

    .top-area { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 32px; }

    .icon {
      width: 64px; height: 64px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b, #ef4444);
      border-radius: 16px; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: 16px; box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(245,158,11,0.4); font-size: 28px;
    }

    .top-area h1 { color: #fff; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; }

    .notice {
      background: rgba(245,158,11,0.15); border: 1px solid rgba(245,158,11,0.4);
      border-radius: 10px; color: #fcd34d; font-size: 13px;
      padding: 12px 16px; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .form-group { margin-bottom: 16px; }

    label {
      display: block; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
      font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    input {
      width: 100%; padding: 13px 16px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
      border-radius: 10px; color: #fff; font-size: 15px;
      transition: border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s; outline: none;
    }

    input::placeholder { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.25); }
    input:focus { border-color: #4f7cff; background: rgba(79,124,255,0.1); }

    .btn-submit {
      width: 100%; padding: 14px; margin-top: 8px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4f7cff, #9b59b6);
      border: none; border-radius: 10px; color: #fff;
      font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; transition: opacity 0.2s;
    }

    .btn-submit:hover { opacity: 0.88; }

    .error-msg {
      background: rgba(255,82,82,0.15); border: 1px solid rgba(255,82,82,0.4);
      border-radius: 8px; color: #ff8080; font-size: 13px;
      padding: 10px 14px; margin-top: 14px; text-align: center;
    }

    .btn-skip {
      display: block; text-align: center; margin-top: 16px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35); font-size: 13px;
      text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.2s;
    }

    .btn-skip:hover { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="top-area">
        <div class="icon">&#128274;</div>
        <h1>비밀번호 변경</h1>
      </div>

      <% if (user.mustChangePw) { %>
      <div class="notice">
        초기 비밀번호로 로그인하셨습니다.<br>
        보안을 위해 새 비밀번호로 변경해 주세요.
      </div>
      <% } %>

      <form method="POST" action="/change_password">
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="current">현재 비밀번호</label>
          <input type="password" id="current" name="current"
                 placeholder="현재 비밀번호를 입력하세요" autocomplete="current-password" required>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="newPw">새 비밀번호</label>
          <input type="password" id="newPw" name="newPw"
                 placeholder="새 비밀번호 (4자 이상)" autocomplete="new-password" required>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="confirm">새 비밀번호 확인</label>
          <input type="password" id="confirm" name="confirm"
                 placeholder="새 비밀번호를 다시 입력하세요" autocomplete="new-password" required>
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn-submit">비밀번호 변경</button>
        <% if (error) { %>
          <div class="error-msg"><%= error %></div>
        <% } %>
      </form>

      <% if (!user.mustChangePw) { %>
        <a class="btn-skip" href="<%= user.role === 'admin' ? '/admin' : '/main' %>">취소</a>
      <% } else { %>
        <a class="btn-skip" href="/logout">로그아웃</a>
      <% } %>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
